<br>
The new msg does have a bug I've noticed tho.  Had bard mez land earlier today on a Creeper.   Worked fine for 3 secs, then get the message &quot;Chali has awakened Mr. Creeper&quot;.   Turn to look, Creeper still mez'd.  Never had him targeted after the mez landed so no idea where the message came from.<br>
